{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01LyV9kS1NGsJh1SQSZSpYnd","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the issue. The changes are:\n\n1. In `server.go`: Increasing the `bufio.Scanner` buffer size to 1MB to handle large log messages from Claude Code\n2. In `handler.go`: Same fix for the web handler's `streamFullLog` function - increasing buffer to 1MB\n3. In `handler_stream_test.go`: A new test that verifies large JSON lines (>64KB, which is the default bufio.Scanner limit) are properly handled\n\nThe root cause: Claude Code can produce JSON log lines larger than 64KB (the default `bufio.Scanner` buffer size). When such a line is encountered, `scanner.Scan()` silently fails and stops reading, causing all subsequent log lines to be dropped. This means logs would stop showing up in the web portal.\n\n\nI should check if the documentation mentions anything about logging or the web portal that might need updating to reflect this buffer size change.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1965,"cache_read_input_tokens":16152,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1965},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"51871dbe-477e-43a1-9c5b-c42af0559400","uuid":"f3b25bcb-de1b-49c4-9d63-8661f7f1c480"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01LyV9kS1NGsJh1SQSZSpYnd","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I understand the bug. The default `bufio.Scanner` buffer is 64KB, but Claude Code can produce JSON log lines exceeding that. When a line is too large, the scanner silently stops, dropping all subsequent log entries. The fix increases the buffer to 1MB in both `server.go` (gRPC tracking) and `handler.go` (web streaming).\n\nNow let me check if any documentation references logging behavior or constraints that need updating."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1965,"cache_read_input_tokens":16152,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1965},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"51871dbe-477e-43a1-9c5b-c42af0559400","uuid":"b25a77b0-7ed4-4b5c-aecf-f82096e19924"}
